                <h1>Every Club.<br><span class="highlight">One Platform.</span></h1>
                <p>Replace scattered group chats, missed emails, and lost tasks. Gryph Club Connect gives every UofG student organization a professional home base — built around the way clubs actually work.</p>
                <div class="hero-ctas">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Started Free →</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-large">See a Demo</button>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-stats">
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="stat-number">UofG</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Only Private Campus</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="stat-number">4</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Core Modules</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="stat-number">5 min</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Setup Time</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="stat-number">Free</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">To Get Started</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-mockup">
                <div class="mockup-preview">
                    <div class="mockup-header">
                        <div class="window-dots">
                            <div class="dot red"></div>
                            <div class="dot gold"></div>
                            <div class="dot green"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mockup-content">
                        <div class="sidebar">
                            <div class="sidebar-section">MY CLUBS</div>
                            <div class="channel-item active">GMA <span class="unread-badge">3</span></div>
                            <div class="channel-item">ESS</div>
                            <div class="channel-item">GFAB</div>
                            <div class="sidebar-section">CHANNELS</div>
                            <div class="channel-item active">#events</div>
                            <div class="channel-item">#general</div>
                            <div class="channel-item">#marketing</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="chat-area">
                            <div class="chat-header">
                                <span># events</span>
                                <span class="online-badge">24 online</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="messages">
                                <div class="message">
                                    <div class="avatar-circle">P</div>
                                    <div><strong>Priya Sharma</strong><br>Winter Gala planning... 🔥</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="message">
                                    <div class="avatar-circle blue">J</div>
                                    <div><strong>James Okafor</strong><br>Venue booking help</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TICKER -->
    <section class="ticker">
        <div class="ticker-scroll">
            <span>● SECURE @UOGUELPH.CA LOGIN ● MULTI-CLUB DASHBOARD ● REAL-TIME CHANNELS ● TASK TRACKING ● EVENT CALENDAR ● RSVP MANAGEMENT ● BUILT FOR GUELPH ●</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROBLEM SECTION -->
    <section class="problem">
        <div class="problem-content">
            <div class="section-eyebrow">THE PROBLEM</div>
            <h2>Your club runs on chaos.</h2>
            <p>Group chats buried in Instagram DMs. Tasks lost in email threads. New members who don't know what's going on.</p>
            <div class="problem-cards">
                <div class="problem-card">
                    <div class="icon">💔</div>
                    <h3>Fragmented Communication</h3>
                    <p>Announcements go to 4 different places. Half your members miss them.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="problem-card">
                    <div class="icon">📋</div>
                    <h3>No Task Accountability</h3>
                    <p>Who was supposed to book the venue? Nobody remembers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="problem-card">
                    <div class="icon">📅</div>
                    <h3>Event Planning Nightmares</h3>
                    <p>Spreadsheets. Texts. Hoping people show up.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FEATURES SECTION -->
    <section class="features" id="features">
        <div class="features-header">
            <div class="section-eyebrow">CORE PLATFORM</div>
            <h2>Everything your club needs, finally in one place.</h2>
            <p>Built specifically for student organizations. Not a social app. Not a generic project tool. A purpose-built club OS.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card red">
                <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
                <div class="feature-tag">COMMUNICATION</div>
                <h3>Team Channels</h3>
                <p>Separate channels for all-hands, exec, marketing, events, and more.</p>
                <a href="#" class="feature-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card gold">
                <div class="feature-icon">✓</div>
                <div class="feature-tag">TASK MANAGEMENT</div>
                <h3>Task Tracker</h3>
                <p>Assign tasks, set deadlines, track progress. Accountability built in.</p>
                <a href="#" class="feature-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card red">
                <div class="feature-icon">📅</div>
                <div class="feature-tag">EVENTS</div>
                <h3>Shared Event Calendar</h3>
                <p>Create events, collect RSVPs, send reminders. One platform for all.</p>
                <a href="#" class="feature-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card gold">
                <div class="feature-icon">👥</div>
                <div class="feature-tag">MEMBERS</div>
                <h3>Member Directory</h3>
                <p>Every member's info—searchable, role-gated, always up to date.</p>
                <a href="#" class="feature-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card red wide">
                <div class="feature-icon">🔄</div>
                <div class="feature-tag">MULTI-CLUB</div>
                <h3>Belong to Multiple Clubs</h3>
                <p>One account. Switch between clubs from a single sidebar. No data mixing.</p>
                <a href="#" class="feature-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card gold">
                <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
                <div class="feature-tag">ADMIN</div>
                <h3>Club Admin Dashboard</h3>
                <p>Monitor engagement, RSVP counts, and channel activity in real-time.</p>
                <a href="#" class="feature-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
    <section class="testimonials" id="testimonials">
        <div class="testimonials-header">
            <div class="section-eyebrow">FROM GUELPH STUDENTS</div>
            <h2>Real clubs. Real results.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonials-grid">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="quote">"We used to run our club through Instagram DMs. Gryph completely changed how we operate — every exec knows what's happening now."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="avatar-circle">P</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Priya Sharma</strong><br>
                        <small>VP Marketing · GMA</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="quote">"As president, the admin dashboard is everything. I can see who's done their tasks and track real engagement."</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="avatar-circle blue">J</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>James Okafor</strong><br>
                        <small>President · Engineering Society</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="quote">"Joining three clubs without confusion is finally possible. One login, one dashboard — I switch between them instantly."</p>
